WEBVTT

00:01:31.821 --> 00:01:35.448
The basic logic is, if you murder someone,

00:01:35.472 --> 00:01:38.163
then you're going to receive
the death penalty.

00:01:39.744 --> 00:01:44.722
So when the jury selection
process took place,

00:01:45.623 --> 00:01:47.142
they asked me,

00:01:49.646 --> 00:01:51.481
"Could you,

00:01:51.505 --> 00:01:57.004
if the evidence presented
justified the death penalty,

00:01:57.028 --> 00:01:59.362
could you deliver,

00:01:59.386 --> 00:02:01.886
rationally and without reservations,